snippet.title: Throwback - Official Early Access Trailer | Upload VR Showcase 2023
snippet.description:
Prepare your arm muscles for Throwback, the paper delivery simulator coming to Steam VR early access in July 2023. Set in a bright retro-futuristic world, you'll need to catch and thow newspapers to build up your highscore.

#SummerOfGaming
